                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and took charge of the prisoner; he said it was his property, and no mistake.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. There is no mark on them, and are fifty public-houses have the same sort of knives and glasses; Grace said she never saw me - I had bought them of a man in the Strand.</p>
               <p>CATHERINE GRACE. I saw his face; I cannot tell what clothes he had on - he had neither shoes nor stockings.</p>
               <p>SAMUEL EVANS. She described him to me before she saw him at the office.</p>
